(719, '311', 'Which component of the pneumatic system provides bleed air to the cabin for pressurization?', 'Cross bleed valve', 'Engine bleed valves', 'Air conditioning packs', 'Wing anti - ice system', 'b', 'Engine bleed valves', 'ERJ-145', 'pneumatic_aircondition_pressurization', 'pilot'),
(720, '312', 'During takeoff, why is it important to close the engine bleed valves?', 'To improve fuel efficiency', 'To prevent contamination of the bleed air', 'To reduce engine wear', 'To increase cabin pressure', 'b', 'To prevent contamination of the bleed air', 'ERJ-145', 'pneumatic_aircondition_pressurization', 'pilot'),
(721, '313', 'Which part of the pneumatic system is responsible for regulating the cabin pressure?', 'Pressure relief valve', 'Bleed air control valve', 'Cabin pressure controller', 'Air cycle machine', 'c', 'Cabin pressure controller', 'ERJ-145', 'pneumatic_aircondition_pressurization', 'pilot'),
