(727, '319', 'Which system provides backup pressurization in case of a failure in the primary pneumatic system?', 'Ram air system', 'Emergency oxygen system', 'Hydraulic system', 'Electrical system', 'a', 'Ram air system', 'ERJ-145', 'pneumatic_aircondition_pressurization', 'pilot'),
